Kathleen Tacchi-Morris (Amụrụ n'ụbọchị 24 Jenụwarị 1899 ruo ụbọchị 12 Mee 1993) bụ onye guzobere Women for World Disarmament (WFWD). Tacchi-Morris bụkwa onye na-agba egwú nke pụtara n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri na-adịghị ekwu okwu, gụnyere Men Are Not Gods (1936). Nna ya bụ onye mepụtara Percy George Tacchi.
A mụrụ Kathleen n'ụbọchị 24 Jenụwarị 1899 Johannesburg, South Africa ma nwụọ na North Curry, Somerset n'ụbọchị 12 Mee 1993. N'oge na-adịghị anya mgbe amuchara ya, ya na ezinụlọ ya laghachiri England.
